description:
Danny welcomes the brilliant and talented Gary Janetti to talk about his hilarious new book (Do You Mind If I Cancel?). They discuss gay influences, favorite divas, the writing process, the importance of gay literature, working on Will and Grace, meeting Brad, Prince George, and lots more. Danny also gives a few book recommendations at the top of the show.


Gary Janetti Interview: 7:53ish
